text: Miloš Klika (3 April 1890 - 21 August 1962) was a Bohemian fencer. He competed in the individual épée and sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1962 deaths Category:Czech male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bohemia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
